<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <view class="hero-eyebrow">Mobile Workspace</view>
    <view class="hero-title">{{userInfo.realName || userInfo.username || '当前用户'}}</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">
      已为当前账号整理出更适合手机场景的高频入口，先把最常用的咨询、签到和周报跑顺，再逐步扩展。
    </view>
    <view class="meta-row">
      <view class="meta-pill">{{accessContext.isAdmin ? '管理员账号' : '授权账号'}}</view>
      <view class="meta-pill">已授权 {{items.length}} 个入口</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel-card">
    <view class="section-title">今日常用</view>
    <view class="section-note">首版先聚焦移动高频动作，不把后台管理全部搬进小程序。</view>
    <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="empty-state">工作台加载中...</view>
    <view wx:else class="tile-grid">
      <button
        wx:for="{{items}}"
        wx:key="key"
        class="tile-button"
        data-path="{{item.path}}"
        bindtap="handleOpen"
      >
        <view class="tile-badge">{{item.badge}}</view>
        <view class="tile-title">{{item.title}}</view>
        <view class="tile-text">{{item.description}}</view>
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
